snippet.title: Big Walk - Reveal Trailer | Game Awards 2023
snippet.description:
From the creators of Untitled Goose Game comes Big Walk, a quirky puzzle game that takes place on a deserted island with a bunch of bizarre looking bird people.

#ign #gaming #thegameawards
